  "text": "from which derives exactly the same result than that of Lemma 3. In particular, the critical value σ c , below which convergence takes place, is again defined by equations (11) and [CITATION_1] . The more remarkable fact here is that this critical value (and hence the convergence rate that comes with it) does not depend on the dimension!",
